entry: Today was honestly one of the best days I’ve had in a while. I woke up early, went for a run, and actually felt energized instead of drained. At work, I finished a project I’d been struggling with, and my manager gave me genuine praise. In the evening, I cooked dinner with my sibling and we laughed the whole time. I feel proud of myself for keeping up with healthy habits and grateful for the small joys that made the day feel light.
